{"tid":327073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【七月飛雹】東京落冰雹手掌咁大！ 傾倒如雪場面觸目驚心","createTime":"2017-07-18T12:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T15:17:08.000Z","uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b65cb8a1a2f183a3f63acf146c28bd64718b2ee","tid":327073,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T12:58:57.000Z","msg":"日本東京都周二下午天氣轉壞雷電交加，多處突然落雹，部分冰雹大如手掌，傾倒如雪，場面觸目驚心。<br />\n<br />\n當地時間下午3時左右，池袋的瀝青路鋪滿相信是雹的冰粒，令地面變成雪白一片。落雹程度之激烈，令人連交通燈也看不見，汽車一度無法動彈。落雹後文京區有住宅的停車場的頂，穿了多個有如手掌大的窿，碎片散落一地。拍片的女子表示：「雹有如波子般大&hellip;&hellip;假如擊中了孩子的話，應該會受傷吧？感到擔心。」<br />\n在JR西日暮里站月台上可以見到，周圍落起幾乎令視野變白的豪雨，有相信是雹的冰粒吹來。拍攝片段的田中健一表示：「還以為是天陰，突然開始落起（雹）來。月台上的人嘗試躲避&hellip;&hellip;突然這樣實在令人恐慌。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170718/large/1500368353_e7e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170718%2Flarge%2F1500368353_e7e4.jpg&h=9ba6c3fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a8fbc085baf6f03b389e6aa93465da7ec210734","tid":327073,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T13:00:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u_5t731j30s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Du_5t731j30s&d=DzMzOM2mnx81MO0OqNJGorIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=954cf80b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u_5t731j30s</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DfTWE5bepik\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDfTWE5bepik&d=DzMzOM2mnx81MO0OqNJGorIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=5fb7a0d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DfTWE5bepik</a>"},{"pid":"04044ec0a64ea2aa976f7b5f7bf5e5bd9dee181b","tid":327073,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T13:04:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XvjaXQg9VWk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=htt